{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/React에서 S3를 이용한 파일 업로드/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Pang's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2ca30100-f0fb-53b7-a62b-ae4ffbbf5364","excerpt":"카메라를 이용하여 알약을 찍어, 이를 무슨 약품인지 확인하는 서비스를 구현하던 도중 이미지를 어떻게 서버에 올렸을 때 가장 효율적일지를 고민하던도중, AWS의 S3 BUCKET을 이용하여 이미지를 업로드하는 방법을 찾아보게되었다.\nS3란 의 약자로 최고의 확장성, 데이터 가용성, 보안 및 성능을 제공하는 객체 스토리지 서비스이다. 일반적인 파일 서버는 트…","html":"<p>카메라를 이용하여 알약을 찍어, 이를 무슨 약품인지 확인하는 서비스를 구현하던 도중 이미지를 어떻게 서버에 올렸을 때 가장 효율적일지를 고민하던도중, AWS의 S3 BUCKET을 이용하여 이미지를 업로드하는 방법을 찾아보게되었다.<br/>\nS3란 <code class=\"language-text\">Simple Storage Service</code>의 약자로 최고의 확장성, 데이터 가용성, 보안 및 성능을 제공하는 객체 스토리지 서비스이다. 일반적인 파일 서버는 트래픽이 증가함에 따라 장비를 증설하는 작업을 해야하는데 S3는 이런 작업을 대행해준다고 한다. 때문에 트래픽에 따른 시스템적 문제를 고민할 필요가 없어지고 접근 권한 또한 설정이 가능하여 보안에도 유리하다.<br/>\nS3에서 사용되는 용어들은 아래와 같다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">객체(Object)</code> : AWS는 S3에 저장된 각각의 데이터를 객체라고 한다</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">버킷(Bucket)</code> : 객체(Object)가 파일이라면 버킷(Bucket)은 연관된 객체들을 그룹핑한 최상위 디렉토리라 할 수 있다. 버킷 단위로 사용 지역을 지정할 수 있고, 버킷에 포함된 모든 객체에 대해서 일괄적으로 인증과 접속 제한을 걸 수 있다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">버전관리</code> : S3에 저장된 객체들의 변화를 저장한다. 예를들어, A라는 객체를 사용자가 삭제하거나 변경해도 각각의 변화를 모두 기록하기 때문에 실수를 돌릴 수 있다.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>1. AWS S3 버킷 생성하기</h2>\n<h3>1-1. 버킷 생성</h3>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/pangs-blog/static/56b927bfc19d0511191c280752fdd7ed/e21a0/1.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 38.82352941176471%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='버킷 만들기' title='버킷 만들기' src='/pangs-blog/static/56b927bfc19d0511191c280752fdd7ed/ca1dc/1.png' srcset='/pangs-blog/static/56b927bfc19d0511191c280752fdd7ed/e7570/1.png 170w,\n/pangs-blog/static/56b927bfc19d0511191c280752fdd7ed/f46e7/1.png 340w,\n/pangs-blog/static/56b927bfc19d0511191c280752fdd7ed/ca1dc/1.png 680w,\n/pangs-blog/static/56b927bfc19d0511191c280752fdd7ed/02d09/1.png 1020w,\n/pangs-blog/static/56b927bfc19d0511191c280752fdd7ed/9d567/1.png 1360w,\n/pangs-blog/static/56b927bfc19d0511191c280752fdd7ed/e21a0/1.png 2052w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>버킷 만들기</figcaption>\n  </figure>\nS3로 이동하여 버킷 만들기를 클릭한다.\n<figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/pangs-blog/static/a8b5f3f0c755c134c7f4c2834f0ef131/a7903/2.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 54.70588235294118%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='버킷 이름' title='버킷 이름' src='/pangs-blog/static/a8b5f3f0c755c134c7f4c2834f0ef131/ca1dc/2.png' srcset='/pangs-blog/static/a8b5f3f0c755c134c7f4c2834f0ef131/e7570/2.png 170w,\n/pangs-blog/static/a8b5f3f0c755c134c7f4c2834f0ef131/f46e7/2.png 340w,\n/pangs-blog/static/a8b5f3f0c755c134c7f4c2834f0ef131/ca1dc/2.png 680w,\n/pangs-blog/static/a8b5f3f0c755c134c7f4c2834f0ef131/02d09/2.png 1020w,\n/pangs-blog/static/a8b5f3f0c755c134c7f4c2834f0ef131/a7903/2.png 1219w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>버킷 이름</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n개인이 사용할 버킷명을 설정해준다(유일한 이름으로)\n<figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/pangs-blog/static/016405be1f7ba05c422d37abfe024cf5/75b60/3.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 83.52941176470588%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='퍼블릭 액세스' title='퍼블릭 액세스' src='/pangs-blog/static/016405be1f7ba05c422d37abfe024cf5/ca1dc/3.png' srcset='/pangs-blog/static/016405be1f7ba05c422d37abfe024cf5/e7570/3.png 170w,\n/pangs-blog/static/016405be1f7ba05c422d37abfe024cf5/f46e7/3.png 340w,\n/pangs-blog/static/016405be1f7ba05c422d37abfe024cf5/ca1dc/3.png 680w,\n/pangs-blog/static/016405be1f7ba05c422d37abfe024cf5/02d09/3.png 1020w,\n/pangs-blog/static/016405be1f7ba05c422d37abfe024cf5/75b60/3.png 1210w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>퍼블릭 액세스</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n모든 퍼블릭 액세스 차단을 풀어주고 버킷을 생성한다.</p>\n<h2>2. 버킷 정책 설정해주기</h2>\n<h3>2-1. 정책 설정하기</h3>\n<p>버킷 생성이 끝났다면 <code class=\"language-text\">버킷 -> 권한 -> 버킷 정책</code>을 설정해줘야한다.\n<a href=\"http://awspolicygen.s3.amazonaws.com/policygen.html\">버킷 정책 생성 URL</a><br/>\n<figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 73.52941176470587%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='버킷 정책' title='버킷 정책' src='/pangs-blog/static/a8e43f8e473cd06da9e2df353afeb4ab/ca1dc/4.png' srcset='/pangs-blog/static/a8e43f8e473cd06da9e2df353afeb4ab/e7570/4.png 170w,\n/pangs-blog/static/a8e43f8e473cd06da9e2df353afeb4ab/f46e7/4.png 340w,\n/pangs-blog/static/a8e43f8e473cd06da9e2df353afeb4ab/ca1dc/4.png 680w,\n/pangs-blog/static/a8e43f8e473cd06da9e2df353afeb4ab/02d09/4.png 1020w,\n/pangs-blog/static/a8e43f8e473cd06da9e2df353afeb4ab/9d567/4.png 1360w,\n/pangs-blog/static/a8e43f8e473cd06da9e2df353afeb4ab/e3039/4.png 1645w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>버킷 정책</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n위 URL에서 정책을 설정해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">Select Type of Policy <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> S3 Bucket Policy\n\nEffect <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Allow\n\nPrincipal <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> *\n\nAWS Service <span class=\"token operator\">:</span>  Amazon S3\n\nActions <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> s3<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>GetObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s3<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>PutObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s3<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>PutObjectAcl (원하는 것을 추가로 선택 가능)\n\n\nAmazon Resource Name (ARN) <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> arn<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>aws<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>s3<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span>bucket-name<span class=\"token comment\">/*</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위와 같이 설정해주고, Generate Policy를 누른다.\n그 후 생성된 JSON값을 버킷 정책에 입력해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Version\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2012-10-17\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Policy1690443207013\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"Statement\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Sid\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Stmt1690443201115\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Effect\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Allow\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Principal\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"*\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Action\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"s3:GetObject\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"s3:PutObject\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"s3:PutObjectAcl\"</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Resource\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"arn:aws:s3:::bucket-name/*\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>나는 위와 같은 형식으로 버킷 정책을 설정해주었다.</p>\n<h3>2-2. CORS 설정하기</h3>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/pangs-blog/static/45ec4dce774ec1ed399f0010f2f06194/2bae1/5.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 34.705882352941174%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAHCAYAAAAIy204AAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAg0lEQVQoz6WRywrEIAxF/f8v7bQLK/Ud9dYELFJmZQOHxICHRNV+HNi2n8C1915wjBs42J61DQgxIeeMNMHnGCOuy0KVUqRRawUH53+UDpVet4b2goOIEEKAYpk+T6SU8SWGuAsJxpinucJ8V4Raaxl5VfoSZnn0Wbi6sgjHZ3xZeeYGHZUpNpBD66UAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='CORS' title='CORS' src='/pangs-blog/static/45ec4dce774ec1ed399f0010f2f06194/ca1dc/5.png' srcset='/pangs-blog/static/45ec4dce774ec1ed399f0010f2f06194/e7570/5.png 170w,\n/pangs-blog/static/45ec4dce774ec1ed399f0010f2f06194/f46e7/5.png 340w,\n/pangs-blog/static/45ec4dce774ec1ed399f0010f2f06194/ca1dc/5.png 680w,\n/pangs-blog/static/45ec4dce774ec1ed399f0010f2f06194/02d09/5.png 1020w,\n/pangs-blog/static/45ec4dce774ec1ed399f0010f2f06194/9d567/5.png 1360w,\n/pangs-blog/static/45ec4dce774ec1ed399f0010f2f06194/2bae1/5.png 2308w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>CORS</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n<code class=\"language-text\">권한 탭의 CORS</code>를 설정해줘야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"AllowedHeaders\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"*\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"AllowedMethods\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"HEAD\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"GET\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"PUT\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"POST\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"DELETE\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"AllowedOrigins\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"*\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"ExposeHeaders\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>다음과 같이 설정한 후 <code class=\"language-text\">ACL(액세스 제어 목록)</code>에서 편집 버튼을 눌러\n<figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/pangs-blog/static/7d59cf3358c755386d8e667490d4998f/baa93/6.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 82.3529411764706%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='ACL 편집' title='ACL 편집' src='/pangs-blog/static/7d59cf3358c755386d8e667490d4998f/ca1dc/6.png' srcset='/pangs-blog/static/7d59cf3358c755386d8e667490d4998f/e7570/6.png 170w,\n/pangs-blog/static/7d59cf3358c755386d8e667490d4998f/f46e7/6.png 340w,\n/pangs-blog/static/7d59cf3358c755386d8e667490d4998f/ca1dc/6.png 680w,\n/pangs-blog/static/7d59cf3358c755386d8e667490d4998f/02d09/6.png 1020w,\n/pangs-blog/static/7d59cf3358c755386d8e667490d4998f/baa93/6.png 1236w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>ACL 편집</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n다음과 같이 설정해준후 <code class=\"language-text\">변경 사항 저장</code>으로 저장한 후 나가준다.</p>\n<h2>3. 액세스 키 생성</h2>\n<p>액세스 키는 모든 퍼블릭 액세스를 차단했을 경우 필요하며, S3에 접근하려면 별도의 인증 과정이 필요하다. 이떄 사용하는 것이 액세스 키이다. 액세스 키는 <code class=\"language-text\">AWSAccessKeyID</code>와<code class=\"language-text\">AWSSecretKey로</code> 구성되어 있다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">보안 자격증명 -> 액세스 키</code>에서 확인 및 생성이 가능하다.\n이때 <code class=\"language-text\">AWSAccessKeyID</code>와<code class=\"language-text\">AWSSecretKey로</code>는 절대 <code class=\"language-text\">외부로 새어 나가면 안되기 때문</code>에 항상 env파일등의 보관하여 보안을 철저히 하도록한다.<br/>\nReact에서 S3를 이용하여 업로드하는 방법은 다음 게시물에 작성하도록 하겠다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bamdule.tistory.com/177\">참고 블로그1</a>,\n<a href=\"https://itprogramming119.tistory.com/entry/React-S3%EB%A5%BC-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%9C-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%97%85%EB%A1%9C%EB%93%9C-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">참고 블로그2</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"AWS S3 생성하기","date":"August 03, 2023","update":"August 03, 2023","tags":["ReactJS","AWS","Blog","S3"],"series":"AWS"},"fields":{"slug":"/React에서 S3를 이용한 파일 업로드/","readingTime":{"minutes":5.035}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"2ca30100-f0fb-53b7-a62b-ae4ffbbf5364","fields":{"slug":"/React에서 S3를 이용한 파일 업로드/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AWS S3 생성하기"}}}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/fullpage사용하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"fullpage.js 사용하기"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/S3 파일업로드/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Next에서 WebCam으로 S3로 이미지 업로드하기"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"2ca30100-f0fb-53b7-a62b-ae4ffbbf5364","series":"AWS","previousPostId":"970f8e13-d64c-5dd4-be56-f5904903fe1b","nextPostId":"76efab50-bd3a-5170-9eb0-50e37f8944e2"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}